(2083, 119, 'sizing_guide_content', '<h2 style="text-align: center;">SIZE CHART</h2>\r\n<p><span style="color: #151515; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">W O M E N \' S Â  S I Z I N G Â  G U I D E</span></p>\r\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1856" src="http://north.fuelthemes.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/sizing_popup.jpg" alt="sizing_popup" width="1316" height="304" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #151515; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">P L E A S E Â  N O T E</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 300;">With all his cruel ferocity and coldness there was an under of something in Tars Tarkas which he seemed ever battling to subdue. Could it be a vestige of some human instinct come back from an ancient forbear to haunt him with the horror of his people\'s ways!</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 300;">As each brand varies in sizing and cut please contact <strong>north@fuelthemes.net</strong> with specific sizing questions.</span></p>'),
